flowchart TD
    Start[Bill Submission Received] --> AutoReject{Auto-Reject Check<br/>AI 99% accuracy}

    AutoReject -->|YES| RejectedFinal1[REJECTED FINAL]
    AutoReject -->|NO| Diagnosis[Multi-Issue Diagnosis<br/>Bill Processor + AI<br/><br/>For each reason:<br/>• Touches Invoice? Y/N<br/>• Requires Dept Action? Y/N]

    Diagnosis --> Split{Split Reasons}
    Split -->|External| ExternalReasons[External Reasons<br/>No dept work<br/>Status: Unresolved]
    Split -->|Internal| InternalReasons[Internal Reasons<br/>Require dept work]

    InternalReasons --> DeptRouting[Route to Departments<br/>Care / Compliance / Accounts<br/><br/>Department performs:<br/>• Reviews<br/>• Contacts parties<br/>• Makes decisions<br/><br/>NO hard timeouts]

    DeptRouting --> ReasonStatus[Reason Status After Work:<br/>• Resolved<br/>• Unresolved<br/>• Awaiting]

    ExternalReasons --> Temporal
    ReasonStatus --> Temporal[Temporal Re-validation<br/><br/>Re-check:<br/>• Funding balance<br/>• Funding period dates<br/>• Authorization status<br/>• Supplier status<br/><br/>May ADD new reasons]

    Temporal --> NewReasons{New Reasons<br/>Added?}

    NewReasons -->|YES| Diagnosis
    NewReasons -->|NO| AnyUnresolved{Any Reason<br/>Still Unresolved?}

    AnyUnresolved -->|NO| AllResolved[All Resolved]
    AllResolved --> Payment[PAID]

    AnyUnresolved -->|YES| CoexistFilter[Can Coexist Filter<br/><br/>Determine which reasons<br/>to include in comms<br/><br/>Apply dominance rules<br/>e.g. Supplier terminated<br/>hides other reasons]

    CoexistFilter --> LimitedTimeWarning[Limited Time Soft Warning<br/>Identification<br/><br/>Check for time-sensitive qualifiers:<br/>• Funding close to depletion<br/>• Authorization nearing expiry<br/>• Service period ending soon]

    LimitedTimeWarning --> Disqualifies{Any Reason<br/>Disqualifies<br/>Future Attempts?}

    Disqualifies -->|NO| TouchesInvoice{Any Reason<br/>Touches Invoice?}

    TouchesInvoice -->|NO| AwaitingExternal{Any Reason<br/>Status = Awaiting<br/>External Action?}

    %% THREE COMMS TYPE NODES
    Disqualifies -->|YES| RejectPeriodType[COMMS TYPE:<br/>REJECT PERIOD]
    TouchesInvoice -->|YES| RejectResubmitType[COMMS TYPE:<br/>REJECT-RESUBMIT]
    AwaitingExternal -->|YES| OnHoldType[COMMS TYPE:<br/>ON HOLD]
    AwaitingExternal -->|NO| RejectPeriodType

    %% REJECT PERIOD PATH - LEFT SIDE
    RejectPeriodType --> CommsPeriod[Draft & Send<br/>REJECT PERIOD Comms<br/><br/>Payload includes:<br/>• Primary blocker reason<br/>• ALL other issues for<br/>  future reference<br/>• NO resubmit link<br/><br/>Split by recipient:<br/>• Supplier / Client / Coordinator]

    CommsPeriod --> RejectedFinal2[REJECTED FINAL<br/><br/>Permanent rejection<br/>Do not resubmit]

    %% REJECT-RESUBMIT PATH - MIDDLE
    RejectResubmitType --> LimitedTimeSoftWarning1[Limited Time - Soft Warning<br/>if applicable<br/><br/>Add urgency notice if:<br/>Time-sensitive qualifiers detected]

    LimitedTimeSoftWarning1 --> CommsReject[Draft & Send<br/>REJECT-RESUBMIT Comms<br/><br/>Payload includes:<br/>• ALL external-facing issues<br/>• Resubmit link<br/>• Soft warning if applicable<br/><br/>Split by recipient:<br/>• Supplier / Client / Coordinator]

    CommsReject --> RejectedResubmit[REJECTED RESUBMIT<br/><br/>This submission is rejected<br/>Supplier may resubmit<br/>as new linked submission]

    RejectedResubmit -.->|Supplier resubmits<br/>New linked submission| Start

    %% ON HOLD PATH - RIGHT SIDE
    OnHoldType --> LimitedTimeSoftWarning2[Limited Time - Soft Warning<br/>if applicable<br/><br/>Add urgency notice if:<br/>Time-sensitive qualifiers detected]

    LimitedTimeSoftWarning2 --> CommsOnHold[Draft & Send<br/>ON HOLD Comms<br/><br/>Payload includes:<br/>• Awaiting reasons<br/>• No resubmit needed<br/>• Status updates<br/>• Soft warning if applicable<br/><br/>Split by recipient:<br/>• Supplier / Client / Coordinator]

    CommsOnHold --> TriggerCadence[Trigger Cadence<br/><br/>Day 0: Comms sent<br/>Day 3: Reminder<br/>Day 7: Final warning<br/>Day 10: Timeout]

    TriggerCadence --> CadenceOutcome{Outcome?}

    CadenceOutcome -->|External Party<br/>Acts/Resolves| TemporalRecheckOnHold[Temporal Recheck<br/><br/>Re-validate all qualifiers<br/>before proceeding to payment]

    TemporalRecheckOnHold --> RecheckPassOnHold{Passed<br/>Re-validation?}
    RecheckPassOnHold -->|YES| Payment
    RecheckPassOnHold -->|NO - New issues| Diagnosis

    CadenceOutcome -->|Timeout<br/>Day 10| TemporalRecheckTimeout[Temporal Recheck<br/><br/>Re-validate before<br/>timeout rejection]

    TemporalRecheckTimeout --> LimitedTimeSoftWarning1

